mbat </strong>A half-fiend mythic minotaur prefers to fight in melee, making full attacks. The minotaur's first attack with his pick in any round is usually a sunder attempt.</p><p><strong>Morale </strong>The minotaurs fight to the death.</p></div><hr /><div><p><strong>STATISTICS</strong></p></div><hr /><div><p><strong>Str </strong>28, <strong>Dex </strong>18, <strong>Con </strong>23, <strong>Int </strong> 9, <strong>Wis </strong>12, <strong>Cha </strong>14</p><p><strong>Base Atk </strong>+10; <strong>CMB </strong>+20 (+24 sunder); <strong>CMD </strong>34 (36 vs. sunder)</p><p><strong>Feats </strong>Great Fortitude, Greater Sunder, Improved Critical (heavy pick), Improved Sunder, Power Attack, ToughnessM, Weapon Focus (heavy pick), Weapon Specialization (heavy pick)</p><p><strong>Skills </strong>Fly +13, Knowledge (dungeoneering) +8, Linguistics +1, Perception +14, Profession (miner) +14</p><p><strong>Languages </strong>Abyssal, Draconic, Giant</p><p><strong>SQ </strong>armor training 1, maze mastery</p><p><strong>Gear </strong><i>+2 breastplate</i>, <i>+2 adamantine heavy pick</i>, <i>amulet of natural armor +1</i>, <i>belt of mighty constitution +2</i></p></div></section>","img":"modules/statblock-library/assets/Covers/Wrath_of_the_Righteous.jpg","_id":"mz9N9Wbd06zvWbpI"}
